{"tid":1888712,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有關 2019-07-21 新聞","createTime":"2020-02-20T11:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T07:30:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b23e9c7167225cd92b0110174f2f37f815109829","tid":1888712,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:05:11.000Z","msg":"有關 2019-07-21 新聞<br />\n<br />\n元朗無警時分<br />\n黑幫喪毆途人 <br />\n<br />\n何君堯與白衣人握手讚「英雄」 <br />\n<br />\n被鬧警黑合作 總督察兇市民<br />\n<br />\n7.21遊行後爆衝突 <br />\n千警上環亂彈清場 <br />\n<br />\n銀髮族上前線守護孩子<br />\n<br />\n7.21混戰全紀錄<br />\n<br />\n43萬人逼爆港島追究警暴 <br />\n<br />\n售票機放滿散紙 單程票<br />\n<br />\n和理非：誓不與勇武派割席<br />\n<br />\n老中青同行 怒罵林鄭禍港<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩質疑警方變陣挑撥情緒<br />\n<br />\n店東落閘上街：公義最緊要<br />\n<br />\n社工促政治問題政治解決 <br />\n<br />\n反對維穩 社署外設連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n陳伯報案 告盧偉聰知法犯法<br />\n<br />\n點滴：金鐘站天眼包膠防噴漆<br />\n<br />\n6.12中彈失明教師：保留身軀抗爭<br />\n<br />\n警鎖定700示威者 運物資照拉<br />\n<br />\n遊行前 警充公急救站<br />\n<br />\n高永文污衊獨立調查 36醫護炮轟<br />\n<br />\n梁栢賢指官員失民心 問責制崩潰<br />\n<br />\n涼茶媽媽再上街 教林鄭做真慈母<br />\n<br />\n央視警告：香港不能再亂 <br />\n<br />\n西環集中營：<br />\n警民衝突惡化 領事外商指京責任大<br />\n<br />\n================<br />\n<br />\n港聞<br />\n<br />\n獄中失眠焦慮 「悲傷非筆墨能形容」<br />\n<br />\n零裝備穿梭警戒線 她們只想提醒勿濫暴 <br />\n<br />\n許麗明：社工不能爆只能陪伴<br />\n<br />\n壹週刊：六七暴動後最大管治危機 <br />\n<br />\n卜約翰嘆：林鄭砸碎了香港<br />\n<br />\n================<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/archive/index/20190722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Farchive%2Findex%2F20190722&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfS3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=ecdf2301\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Farchive%2Findex%2F20190722&h=de62e9d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/archive/index/20190722</a>"},{"pid":"364513784079005fe16e8cb9723844178628307c","tid":1888712,"uid":123138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a65a2fe67976ff57ff33869d73b431b393cbcc8","tid":1888712,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:08:53.000Z","msg":"暴政嚟"},{"pid":"85cf5d2c4f37efbc3ad5c707e3fedf99113b3f80","tid":1888712,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:12:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"531b7aa70ee09d2d66868863d06edcffa43cfcba","tid":1888712,"uid":123138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e0d182192c11f518d42cce53870dc9d15da2d8","tid":1888712,"uid":171763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:13:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da48643012ab715aad448d2b5477dcb56f14eefa","tid":1888712,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abe12dbb6bb72b7270e08289c6e09a3c4cfa723","tid":1888712,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:30:07.000Z","msg":"［慶祝夠未］警 世 文！一齊打返起文宣戰線好嗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1890283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1890283</a><br />\n- 分享自